xxl.core.collections.queues
Interface FIFOQueue<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the type of the elements of this queue.
All Superinterfaces:
Queue<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayQueue, BlockBasedQueue, CounterRandomAccessFileQueue, ListQueue, ListStreamQueue, RandomAccessFileQueue
public interface FIFOQueue<E>
extends Queue<E>

The interface FIFO queue represents a FIFO (first in, first out) iteration over a collection of elements (also known as a sequence) with a peek method. This interface predefines a FIFO strategy for addition and removal of elements.
